{"tid":1790884,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港最紅國企】 中海集團 - 中國海外發展","createTime":"2019-12-20T10:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T06:50:38.000Z","uid":68491,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8bcd4ef58774c761ef5b93da061642d88c069e7d","tid":1790884,"uid":68491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:26:57.000Z","msg":"頭先食飯行經軒尼詩道仲見到中銀封晒板，但隔離<span style=\"color: red;\">中國海外大廈</span>仲係十分光鮮，諗極都唔明點解明明<span style=\"color: red;\">中海集團</span>係國務院下既國家企業反而唔夠中銀慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n純粹覺得搞笑開post。<br />\n<br />\n簡單介紹下大家所認識/唔認識係香港最紅既國企:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國務院 &gt; 中國建築集團有限公司 &gt; 中國海外集團有限公司</span></span> &gt; 中國海外發展有限公司  688 &gt; 中海物業 2669，中國建議工程(香港) 3311 &gt; 中國建築地基 等等<br />\n<br />\n只係十分簡化版，仲有常見既中海保安，遠東，中海投資等等，多到根本數唔哂。<br />\n<br />\n你話中國建築接到咁多機場地盤，mtr，西九job唔係有紅色傾向我真係唔信，呢啲ICAC又唔走去查，831又唔查，到底ICAC仲係咪有人做緊野都成問題。"},{"pid":"ae8148077e889b16b2458b5a1d390ab682164fb2","tid":1790884,"uid":1891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:27:44.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n1221<br />\n721後嘅五個月<br />\n香港人有忘記嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccF7Pwj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccF7Pwj.jpg&h=a4c97012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XcqBbk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XcqBbk.png&h=b08a4737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPEkp4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPEkp4G.jpg&h=82652877&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27b6d1788293999f190814b64c6bccfff96a5380","tid":1790884,"uid":68491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bcd4ef58774c761ef5b93da061642d88c069e7d","tid":1790884,"uid":68491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:26:57.000Z","msg":"頭先食飯行經軒尼詩道仲見到中銀封晒板，但隔離<span style=